oda-data-set.name: Data Set
oda-data-set.xml-property: select * from CLASSICMODELS.CUSTOMERS, CLASSICMODELS.ORDERS, CLASSICMODELS.ORDERDETAILS, CLASSICMODELS.PRODUCTS where CLASSICMODELS.CUSTOMERS.CUSTOMERNUMBER=CLASSICMODELS.ORDERS.CUSTOMERNUMBER and CLASSICMODELS.ORDERS.ORDERNUMBER=CLASSICMODELS.ORDERDETAILS.ORDERNUMBER and CLASSICMODELS.ORDERDETAILS.PRODUCTCODE=CLASSICMODELS.PRODUCTS.PRODUCTCODE
